  <h2><a href="../node/108" title="HSNL featured in Christian Science Monitor">HSNL featured in Christian Science Monitor</a></h2>

      <span class="submitted">Fri, 01/23/2009 - 16:13 — Matt Welsh</span>
  
  <div class="content clear-block">
    The <a href="http://www.csmonitor.com">Christian Science Monitor</a> published an article today entitled <a href="http://features.csmonitor.com/innovation/2009/01/23/new-networks-take-nature%E2%80%99s-pulse/">"New Networks take Nature's Pulse"</a> that features work done by our lab, including the <a href="http://fiji.eecs.harvard.edu/blog/Volcano">volcano monitoring</a> and <a href="http://www.citysense.net">CitySense</a> projects.  </div>

