  <h2><a href="../node/69" title="Flask paper accepted to ICFP 2008">Flask paper accepted to ICFP 2008</a></h2>

      <span class="submitted">Mon, 07/14/2008 - 15:58 — Matt Welsh</span>
  
  <div class="content clear-block">
    Our paper, <a href="http://fiji.eecs.harvard.edu/blog/biblio/citekey/flask">Flask: Staged Functional Programming for Sensor Networks</a>, has been accepted to the <a href="http://www.icfpconference.org/icfp2008/">International Conference on Functional Programming</a> (ICFP 2008), to be held in British Columbia in September 2008! <a href="http://www.eecs.harvard.edu/~mdw/papers/flask-icfp08.pdf">Full text available here.</a>  </div>

